-"experiments/minif2f_v4/src/bin/evaluator.rs" = "0263e7f318c01144473c9a6b3a6c5d9250c2e65b16027f8e7a85ac9db0f9ef9e"  # rehashed by TB-G G3.3 (2026-05-12; charter §1 Module G3 atom G3.3; G-Phase directive §G3 verbatim 7-field `AgentMarketState` shape + Drucker framing): per-viewer `=== Your Position ===` block wired at the build_agent_prompt site (~line 2204; AFTER pending_peer_reviews render, BEFORE build_agent_prompt call). Renders the viewer's own balance + open positions + realized/unrealized PnL + solvency + reputation via `turingosv4::sdk::your_position::render_your_position(&q, &AgentId(agent_id.clone()))` against the sequencer's `q_snapshot()`. Per-viewer isolation enforced by `compute_agent_pnl(q, viewer, ...)` (filters EconomicState slices by `viewer` identity; never aggregates across agents per Art. III.4 shielding). Empty-string-suppression contract mirrors econ_position + pending_peer_reviews — when bus.sequencer is None (legacy WAL-only mode), the block is suppressed. `build_agent_prompt` call updated to pass `&your_position` as the new 10th argument. Predecessor TB-G G2.1 hash 4a369b4f superseded.  # rehashed by TB-G G2.1 (2026-05-12; charter §1 Module G2 atom G2.1; G-Phase directive §G2 verbatim 9-variant `enum NoTradeReason`; SG-G2.6 trace-or-tx invariant wire): (1) market-context build site (~line 2106) gains two boolean witnesses captured during the TB-N3 same-task pool render — `tb_n3_market_block_present` (was `tb_n3_block` non-empty in the rendered prompt) + `tb_n3_market_block_budget_elided` (`TURINGOS_TB_N3_MARKET_CONTEXT_K = 0` forced top-K=0 elision while same-task pools existed). (2) parse-match site (~line 2291) gains `invest_action_emitted_this_turn` flag set true at the head of the `"invest"` dispatch arm. (3) NEW end-of-turn classifier between the parse-match close and the LLM-error arm: if `!invest_action_emitted_this_turn && (tb_n3_market_block_present || tb_n3_market_block_budget_elided)`, fires `MarketDecisionTrace::no_trade(NoTradeReason::NoPerceivedEdge | NoTradeReason::PromptBudgetExceeded, …)` to CAS via `write_market_decision_trace_to_cas` + bumps `tool_dist["invest_no_trade_<label>"]` counter. Closes the trace-or-tx invariant gap: every non-invest market-bearing agent turn now leaves a classifier-bound CAS trace, satisfying SG-G2.6 alongside the existing `"invest"` arm's Submitted / NoTrade dispatch. Predecessor TB-G G2P.1 hash b5c5ec97 superseded.  # rehashed by TB-G G2P.1 (2026-05-12; charter §1 Module G2P atom G2P.1; G-Phase directive §0.6 amendment G-2 "verify_peer=0 比 invest=0 更危险"; closes user 2026-05-12 病灶3 "0 verify"): per-viewer Pending Peer Reviews block wired at the build_agent_prompt site (~line 2188; AFTER econ_position render, BEFORE build_agent_prompt call). Renders queue of accepted peer WorkTxs eligible for this viewer's verify_peer action by calling `turingosv4::sdk::pending_peer_reviews::render_pending_peer_reviews(&q, &AgentId(agent_id.clone()), DEFAULT_PENDING_REVIEWS_K)` against the sequencer's q_snapshot. Empty-string-suppression contract mirrors econ_position. build_agent_prompt signature gains 9th `pending_peer_reviews: &str` arg; the new block lands under canonical "=== Pending Peer Reviews ===" heading in src/sdk/prompt.rs. Pure-read of canonical EconomicState.stakes_t + agent_verifications_t; no private CoT / attempt_telemetry / proposal_cid reads (CLAUDE.md §15 selective shielding). Predecessor TB-N3 A3+A4 hash 36b550c9 superseded.  # rehashed by TB-N3 A3 + A4 hookup (2026-05-11; architect ruling 2026-05-11 amendments 3-6 + Q1+Q2+Q6 + Q7 + amendment 5): (1) full-proof OMEGA WorkTx accept site (post tb8_await_state_root_advance ~line 2772) + per-tactic OMEGA WorkTx accept site (~line 3661) BOTH gain a `TURINGOS_TB_N3_AUTO_MARKET=1`-gated call to `tb_n3_emit_node_market_after_work_accept(&bundle.sequencer, &work_tx_id, &mut reg, "a3-omega-{work_tx_id}", logical_t, seed_micro)` — outcome typed-matched (Created/AlreadyExists/BudgetExhausted/SubmitFailed/PollTimeo